U.K. Stocks Decline for Sixth Day; FTSE 100 Index Drops 0.7% in London

-- B y   S a r a h   J o n e s
-- 
2011-03-16T10:12:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-16/u-k-stocks-decline-for-sixth-day-benchmark-ftse-100-index-drops-0-7-.html
U.K. stocks dropped for a sixth
day, the longest stretch of declines for the FTSE 100 Index
since January 2009.  The benchmark FTSE 100 retreated 0.7 percent to 5,655.78 at
10:09 a.m. in  London , extending it’s decline since  Japan ’s
earthquake on March 11 to 3.2 percent.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Sarah Jones at 
 sjones35@bloomberg.net  